# Schema Mapper — Cursor Rules

This is a Sanity App SDK application using React Flow for schema visualization.

## Key Patterns
- Sanity App SDK hooks: useProjects(), useDatasets(), useClient(), useDashboardOrganizationId()
- ResourceProvider wraps per-project/dataset context
- React Flow: custom nodes (SchemaNode), custom edges (GentleBezierEdge), ELK/dagre layout
- Module-level mutable variables (_curvature, _spacing, _edgeStyle) for edge component config
- Tailwind CSS v4 for styling, Sanity UI for tabs/dialogs/spinners

## Important
- Hook ordering matters: useCallback referencing setEdges must come AFTER useEdgesState
- Node types and edge types must be defined OUTSIDE React components
- useDatasets() fails for projects without membership — always wrap in ErrorBoundary
- ResourceProvider needs fallback={null} prop
- sanity must be in devDependencies, not dependencies

## File Structure
- src/components/LiveOrgOverview.tsx — data orchestration
- src/components/OrgOverview.tsx — main UI
- src/components/SchemaGraph.tsx — React Flow graph + layout engines
- src/components/SchemaNode.tsx — custom node component
- src/hooks/useSchemaDiscovery.ts — schema inference from document sampling
